\newlabel{fig:heuristic-baseline}{{2a}{4}{Heuristic-bot baseline. The heuristic-bot, designed to be aligned with the benchmark, played 10, 3-player games with itself and scored a task success rate of 100\% in each game}{figure.caption.6}{}}
\newlabel{sub@fig:heuristic-baseline}{{a}{4}{Heuristic-bot baseline. The heuristic-bot, designed to be aligned with the benchmark, played 10, 3-player games with itself and scored a task success rate of 100\% in each game}{figure.caption.6}{}}
\newlabel{fig:react-comparison}{{2b}{4}{ReAct-agent comparison. the ReAct GPT-4o agent defeated the heuristic-bot. Despite having a lower task success rate than the heuristic-bot, the ReAct agent achieved a higher overall score due to its superior win rate and final victory points, demonstrating that task success rate is not the sole determinant of performance in CatanBench}{figure.caption.6}{}}
